The following format should be used in the CoScale UI:

	{"action":"{ACTION}","token":"8d8efa2f-5fde-4d08-bb2d-6d227439e399","server":"{SUBJECT}"}


The webhook can be tested with the following curl:

	curl -X POST -d '{"action":"triggered","token":"8d8efa2f-5fde-4d08-bb2d-6d227439e399","server":"k8s_api_cs-api-ttq25_default_179592fc-2c1a-11e7-8f45-000d3a27567d"}' http://localhost/debug/heapdump